name: Warrant Officer M'Kae (V)
Lore: 'Hard-working Avenger signal officer. Coordinates and tests tractor beam operations. Apprises Executor of his ship''s activities and relays orders from the flagship to his captain.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. If your starship is about to be lost, may place devices aboard in owner''s Used Pile. Once per turn, may deploy a device that deploys on a starship from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Once per game, if just forfeited, may take the bottom card of your Lost Pile into hand.',
